304
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,240
Well, do others dare to do this?

305
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,200
Here.

306
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,480
Here.

307
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,120
No.

308
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,840
No.

309
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,800
No.

310
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,280
No.

311
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,640
No.

312
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,280
No.

313
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:54,760
Wait.

314
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:03,000
Damn, you’re heavily made up.

315
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:05,240
Hey, not really.

316
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,560
That’s just social media level.

317
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:10,960
You have to wear makeup like this so people will swipe...

318
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:11,960
