325
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:28,160
Whoa, no makeup.

326
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,640
Bareface trend, huh...

327
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:33,440
Well, you need a good face first before going bare.

328
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,920
Whoa, this is too bare.

329
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:37,240
Chaba, help me out!

330
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:39,280
Sorry, I really can’t side with you on this one.

331
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:41,480
Your real face is a mess.

332
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,760
Bitch, I’m your friend!

333
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:45,920
And you’re saying that photo doesn’t look like me?

334
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,920
Nope. It looks like smeared makeup on someone’s foot.

335
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:57,320
Two years ago, Glam sent people to mess with my airline.

336
00:17:57,320 --> 00:18:00,320
Even now, I still got a scar from that.

337
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:06,160
