340
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:16,360
To see if it still measures up to compete with Glamorous Airline.

341
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:21,000
It’s all tidy here.

342
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:24,000
Even that random box in the middle of the cabin is neatly placed.

343
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:29,880
Oh no, oh no.

344
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:32,040
Wait, it could just be an ordinary box.

345
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,240
Don’t panic.

346
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:36,360
You're the most panicked person on this plane right now.

347
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:38,680
You don’t need to call anyone.

348
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:42,680
