359
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:32,360
We’ll all be wiped out at once, Madam.

360
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:33,360
We’ll talk about it later.

361
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,680
I remember that sound clearly.

362
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,880
No.

363
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:54,720
I checked the records.

364
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:58,720
Two years ago, there were no incidents of bomb-planting on Porn Airline.

365
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:02,480
Right, it’s not a bomb.

366
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:05,160
It’s a clock for sure, old gag.

367
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,240
It's a box of donuts.

368
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,320
Donuts?

369
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:10,240
Someone placed a box of donuts.

370
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,200
So what about the sound?

371
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:14,960
It was the sound of my wristwatch.

372
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,880
When I lifted the donut box like this,

373
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,640
