sent someone to sabotage you, you’re guessing...

376
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:34,280
Well, a donut box shouldn’t be that black.

377
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:35,920
And even if it’s not a bomb,

378
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:39,360
a box of donuts sitting in the middle of the cabin like that,

379
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:41,280
it’s obvious someone put it there on purpose.

380
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:44,280
That’s why my flight was delayed and the company got damaged.

381
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,280
And how do you know Glam sent it?

382
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:52,560
I’m really sorry.

383
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:55,480
I didn’t mean to cause any trouble for your airline.

384
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:57,120
I must have accidentally dropped it there.

385
00:20:57,120 --> 00:21:00,040
It’s okay. The flight’s delayed anyway.

386
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,040
Would you like one?

387
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:13,080
Ah!

388
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,320
What’s that sound?

389
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:23,320
My phone. I put it in the box.

390
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:24,560
Someone just happened to call me.

391
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,680
Excuse me, I need to take this.

392
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,800
Hey, wait, you, wait!

393
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:34,000
Siri, follow him!

394
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:34,400
Wait, wait!

395
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,320
Go, Siri!

396
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,080
Don’t go yet.

397
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:37,080
Why not?

398
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,920
