399
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:55,080
Siri! Nurse!

400
00:21:57,120 --> 00:22:01,120
I saw with my own eyes that Glam called that number.

401
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,480
No.

402
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:06,040
I checked Glam’s call logs from that day.

403
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:08,480
He didn’t call anyone that day.

404
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:10,080
You have all that info?

405
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:12,080
Glam might not have only one number.

406
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:20,960
Whatever the number is, there’s no way Glam could’ve called anyone.

407
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,800
Because he was in Tibet that day.

408
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:26,720
And someone named Glam isn’t unique in this world.

409
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:30,720
