410
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,120
And he tried to hurt me too.

411
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:33,400
What did he do to hurt you?

412
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:36,800
He scared me so badly my head hit the seat.

413
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:40,560
My head split. It left a scar that’s still here every day.
Look.

414
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:40,960
I don’t see it.

415
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:43,560
Look closer.
See it there?

416
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:44,560
I don’t see it.

417
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:48,360
Look closer.
It's right here.

418
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:49,360
I don't see it.

419
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:07,840
I think we should take a break and use the restroom first.

420
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,280
Oh!

421
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:17,760
Uh, the door to the restroom is over there.

422
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:41,240
