426
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:06,600
This airport is smoke-free, including e-cigarettes.

427
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:11,320
Sorry, Sky, Chaba, for calling you in on standby.

428
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:13,600
Lately, we’ve had to add a lot more flights.

429
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:15,760
Because Porn Airline collapsed, right?

430
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:16,760
So passengers had no flights to take.

431
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:21,880
Well, when the owner of the airline
got sentenced to over a thousand years in prison...

432
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:24,160
