No, thanks.

433
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:27,240
True. Serves her right.
She brought it on herself.

434
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:33,280
All-New means the court hasn’t ruled yet.

435
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,600
We don’t know the full truth.

436
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:37,600
All-New, sounds like you’re secretly invested in Madam Porn’s story.

437
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:44,800
And those 284 cases against her...

438
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:45,800
127!

439
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:48,560
She only has 127 cases.

440
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:50,800
