451
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,760
Let’s hurry and board the plane now.

452
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:18,920
Come on, All-New, let’s go.

453
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:33,200
After hearing your whole story, it’s very likely that...

454
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,160
Glam framed me.

455
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:38,920
You’re someone who’s bad at interpreting things
and analyzes everything all wrong.

456
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:41,320
But everything I’ve said is true.

457
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:44,040
Then do this, analyze me.

458
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:50,160
Look at me, study me, and guess what I’m thinking about you.

459
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:54,720
You think I’m some delusional criminal.

460
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:55,880
No.

461
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:56,960
A lying criminal.

462
00:25:57,320 --> 00:25:58,320
No.

463
00:25:58,480 --> 00:25:59,360
A criminal...

464
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:03,360
I think you’re fragile and in need of care.

465
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:06,240
Saying that...

466
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,720
are you trying to tell me something?

467
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:11,120
I’m saying someone like you belongs in prison.

468
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:13,720
So we can keep watching over you all the time.

469
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,880
That’s exactly what Glam wants.

470
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,400
I told you I’m not lying.

471
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:20,040
Everything I’ve said is the truth.

472
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:22,040
Alright, if you want to prove the truth,

473
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:25,600
