Science can test this.

474
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:29,240
Bring in ten lie detectors if you want.

475
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,520
Then allow me.

476
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:33,000
I’ll take your pulse and ask you some questions.

477
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,000
General questions.

478
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:37,960
First question...what’s your favorite color?

479
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,840
Purple.

480
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:39,920
What do you like to eat?

481
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:40,840
Pad Thai.

482
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:42,080
Mountains or sea?

483
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:42,960
Sea.

484
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,200
Favorite flower?

485
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,760
Anthurium.

486
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:47,000
Type of man you like?

487
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,680
Tall.

488
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,160
Mm.

489
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,720
Muscular.

490
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,360
Mm.

491
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:51,880
Thai-looking face.

492
00:26:52,040 --> 00:26:52,640
Mm.

493
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:53,280
Handsome.

494
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:53,680
Mm.

495
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,680
Doctorate degree...

496
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:55,680
Like me...

497
00:26:57,760 --> 00:27:03,160
